  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  persistent AF (electrical cardioversion is planned)

          -  written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  acute clinical signs of venous thromboembolism

          -  current oral anticoagulation

          -  indication for medical cardioversion
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
